{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01TvUFVZBU3amwFJCACLRnkZ","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# Specification Quality Checklist: 203 E2E Integration Tests\n     2→\n     3→**Purpose**: Validate specification completeness and quality before implementation\n     4→**Created**: 2026-02-18\n     5→**Spec**: [spec.md](./spec.md)\n     6→\n     7→---\n     8→\n     9→## Content Quality\n    10→\n    11→- [x] No implementation details (languages, frameworks, APIs)\n    12→- [x] Focused on user value and business needs\n    13→- [x] Written for non-technical stakeholders\n    14→- [x] All mandatory sections completed\n    15→\n    16→## Requirement Completeness\n    17→\n    18→- [x] No [NEEDS CLARIFICATION] markers remain\n    19→- [x] Requirements are testable and unambiguous\n    20→- [x] Success criteria are measurable\n    21→- [x] Success criteria are technology-agnostic\n    22→- [x] Acceptance criteria are defined\n    23→- [x] Edge cases are identified\n    24→- [x] Scope is clearly bounded\n    25→- [x] Dependencies and assumptions identified\n    26→\n    27→## Feature Readiness\n    28→\n    29→- [x] All functional requirements have clear acceptance criteria\n    30→- [x] User scenarios cover primary flows\n    31→- [x] Feature meets measurable outcomes defined in Success Criteria\n    32→- [x] No implementation details leak into specification\n    33→\n    34→---\n    35→\n    36→## Open Items\n    37→\n    38→| # | Item | Category | Blocking? |\n    39→|---|------|----------|-----------|\n    40→| 1 | Resolved: spec now explicitly requires both suites — local deterministic (`pnpm test:e2e`) and real devnet VRF (`pnpm test:e2e:devnet`) | Scope | No |\n    41→| 2 | Track in implementation: validate `solana-test-validator` availability in CI and fail fast when missing | Dependency | No |\n    42→| 3 | Track in implementation: add and validate dual-browser-context fixture for two-player flow | Edge Case | No |\n    43→| 4 | Decide CI trigger policy for devnet suite (nightly vs pre-release gate vs manual) and document owner | Process | No |\n    44→\n    45→## Notes\n    46→\n    47→- Depends on spec 203 E2E infra and spec 205 TestWalletProvider\n    48→- Items marked incomplete require spec updates before implementation\n    49→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_011paUumEGR8dxw4u7sjMLhC","session_id":"f6036e3a-bc98-4f9f-8839-caeed7dcba03","uuid":"03807b5a-52ef-48a3-852d-8bded286451a"}
