{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_014sA3bfSDdUCT16rk6ui4Zr","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Now I have comprehensive information. Let me compile this into a clear report for you.\n\n## Solana Programs Structure - Comprehensive Exploration Report\n\nI've thoroughly explored the Solana workspace in `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/`. Here's what you need to know:\n\n---\n\n### 1. Anchor.toml Configuration\n\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/Anchor.toml`\n\n```toml\n[toolchain]\nanchor_version = \"0.32.1\"\n\n[features]\nresolution = true\nskip-lint = false\n\n[programs.localnet]\ncoinflip = \"BdHFeqmkYe7znXV1Avk3zz496Pjo8QhEDN4MKPUTAWwx\"\nplatform = \"85qwC1cDpSYkBBHUcN4nuZ119hCx4N94X38GjAHxnWjA\"\n\n[programs.devnet]\ncoinflip = \"BdHFeqmkYe7znXV1Avk3zz496Pjo8QhEDN4MKPUTAWwx\"\nplatform = \"85qwC1cDpSYkBBHUcN4nuZ119hCx4N94X38GjAHxnWjA\"\n\n[registry]\nurl = \"https://api.apr.dev\"\n\n[provider]\ncluster = \"Localnet\"\nwallet = \"~/.config/solana/id.json\"\n\n[scripts]\ntest = \"pnpm exec mocha --require tsx/cjs -t 1000000 tests/**/*.ts\"\n```\n\n**Key Settings**:\n- Anchor 0.32.1 (matches memory context)\n- Same program IDs for both localnet and devnet (BdHFe... for coinflip, 85qwC... for platform)\n- Test timeout: 1,000,000ms (16+ min)\n- Uses tsx/cjs for TypeScript test execution\n\n---\n\n### 2. Test File Setup (solana/tests/coinflip.ts) - First 100+ Lines\n\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/tests/coinflip.ts`\n\n**Test Framework**: Mocha + Chai + anchor-bankrun (no live validator)\n\n**Setup Pattern**:\n```typescript\nimport { startAnchor, BankrunProvider } from \"anchor-bankrun\";\nimport { Program, AnchorError, Wallet } from \"@coral-xyz/anchor\";\nimport { Keypair, PublicKey, SystemProgram, LAMPORTS_PER_SOL } from \"@solana/web3.js\";\nimport { Clock } from \"solana-bankrun\";\n\n// Load IDLs from target/idl/ directory\nconst IDL = JSON.parse(readFileSync(join(__dirname, \"..\", \"target\", \"idl\", \"coinflip.json\"), \"utf8\"));\nconst PROGRAM_ID = new PublicKey(IDL.address);\n\nconst PLATFORM_IDL = JSON.parse(readFileSync(join(__dirname, \"..\", \"target\", \"idl\", \"platform.json\"), \"utf8\"));\nconst PLATFORM_PROGRAM_ID = new PublicKey(PLATFORM_IDL.address);\n```\n\n**Key Constants** (matching shared crate):\n```typescript\nconst SIDE_HEADS = 0;\nconst SIDE_TAILS = 1;\nconst TIER_IRON = 0;\nconst TIER_IRON_AMOUNT = 5_000_000; // 0.005 SOL in lamports\nconst TOTAL_FEE_BPS = 300;\nconst DEFAULT_RESOLVE_TIMEOUT = 120; // seconds\n```\n\n**Mock VRF Randomness Buffers** (32 bytes each):\n- `RANDOMNESS_HEADS`: byte[0]=2 → 2%2=0 (HEADS), non-zero = fulfilled\n- `RANDOMNESS_TAILS`: byte[0]=1 → 1%2=1 (TAILS), non-zero = fulfilled\n- `RANDOMNESS_UNFULFILLED`: all zeros = not fulfilled\n\n**PDA Helpers** (seed-based):\n```typescript\ngetMatchPda(creator: PublicKey) → [\"match\", creator]\ngetConfigPda() → [\"coinflip_config\"]\ngetPlatformConfigPda() → [\"platform_config\"]\ngetPlayerProfilePda(wallet: PublicKey) → [\"player_profile\", wallet]\n```\n\n**TestContext Factory** (`createTestContext()`):\n- Generates opponent, treasury, mock VRF accounts (randomness, program, network state, treasury)\n- Calls `startAnchor(\"./\", [], [accounts])` with pre-funded bankrun accounts (100 SOL each)\n- Sets up both creator and opponent `Program<Coinflip>` + `Program<Platform>` instances\n- Returns all PDAs and keypairs needed for test instructions\n\n---\n\n### 3. Program IDs and Keypairs\n\n**Hardcoded Program IDs** (same on localnet + devnet):\n\n| Program | Address |\n|---------|---------|\n| **Coinflip** | `BdHFeqmkYe7znXV1Avk3zz496Pjo8QhEDN4MKPUTAWwx` |\n| **Platform** | `85qwC1cDpSYkBBHUcN4nuZ119hCx4N94X38GjAHxnWjA` |\n\n**Keypair Locations** (after build):\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/target/deploy/coinflip-keypair.json` (227 bytes)\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/target/deploy/platform-keypair.json` (224 bytes)\n\n**Deployed Binaries**:\n- `coinflip.so` — 331,256 bytes\n- `platform.so` — 215,464 bytes\n\n**IDL Files** (generated):\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/target/idl/coinflip.json`\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/target/idl/platform.json`\n\n---\n\n### 4. .so Files in target/ (Complete List)\n\nFound 92 .so files across debug, release, and sbpf targets. **Actively deployed binaries**:\n\n```\nsolana/target/deploy/\n├── coinflip.so (331,256 bytes) — Main program binary\n└── platform.so (215,464 bytes)  — Main program binary\n\nsolana/target/sbpf-solana-solana/release/deps/\n├── solana_program-072e2a1ef7618bd5.so\n├── solana_zk_sdk-25eb3f1a039bc1c1.so\n├── spl_discriminator-c07b80c972b66114.so\n├── spl_program_error-e3176d0118503053.so\n├── spl_pod-cb99b031206112dc.so\n├── spl_type_length_value-10e1b514f6e4e51c.so\n├── spl_token_group_interface-590398a192a381f5.so\n├── spl_memo-1c3bad1b551f9b4f.so\n├── spl_tlv_account_resolution-71ac12ac8a4d56f1.so\n├── spl_elgamal_registry-4307178ba6db05fb.so\n├── spl_transfer_hook_interface-209fa8feb53442a1.so\n... (78 more macro/build-related .so files in debug targets)\n```\n\n---\n\n### 5. Test Scripts and Bootstrap Utilities\n\n**Available Scripts** in `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/scripts/`:\n\n| File | Purpose |\n|------|---------|\n| **deploy-devnet.sh** | Bash script: build + deploy to devnet; validates SBF toolchain v1.52+; checks wallet balance; runs init-devnet-config.ts after deploy |\n| **init-devnet-config.ts** | TypeScript: idempotent config initialization (skips if already created); loads wallet from `~/.config/solana/id.json`; calls `initializePlatform()` + `initializeConfig()` on both programs |\n| **join-devnet-match.ts** | TypeScript: helper to join a match on devnet |\n| **test-devnet-lifecycle.ts** | TypeScript: full integration test lifecycle on devnet |\n\n**Test Files** in `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/tests/`:\n\n| File | Lines | Purpose |\n|------|-------|---------|\n| **coinflip.ts** | 33,120 | Main bankrun tests: init, create match, join, resolve (heads/tails), payout settlement |\n| **platform.ts** | 7,320 | Platform program bankrun tests: initialize, player profiles, fee tracking |\n| **devnet-integration.md** | 2,077 | Documentation (not executable) |\n\n---\n\n### 6. Workspace Structure\n\n**Cargo Workspace** (`solana/Cargo.toml`):\n```toml\n[workspace]\nmembers = [\n    \"shared\",              # Shared lib (not deployed, pure types/helpers)\n    \"programs/coinflip\",   # Coinflip program\n    \"programs/platform\",   # Platform program\n]\n\n[workspace.dependencies]\nanchor-lang = \"0.32.1\"\norao-solana-vrf = { version = \"0.7.0\", features = [\"cpi\"] }\nrng-shared = { path = \"shared\" }\nsolana-sha256-hasher = \"2.3\"\n```\n\n**Program Dependencies**:\n\n| Program | Deps |\n|---------|------|\n| **coinflip** | anchor-lang, rng-shared, platform (w/ cpi feature), orao-solana-vrf |\n| **platform** | anchor-lang, rng-shared, orao-solana-vrf |\n| **shared** | anchor-lang, orao-solana-vrf, solana-sha256-hasher |\n\n**Build Features**:\n- `mock-vrf` (default) — uses mock VRF for local testing\n- `no-default-features` — disables mock-vrf, uses real Orao VRF (for devnet deploy)\n- `cpi` — enables CPI interface (coinflip only, for platform CPI calls)\n\n---\n\n### 7. Key Test Setup Patterns\n\n**Bankrun (No Live Validator)**:\n```typescript\nconst context = await startAnchor(\"./\", [], [\n  { address: opponent.publicKey, info: fundedAccountData(100 * LAMPORTS_PER_SOL) },\n  { address: mockOraoProgram.publicKey, info: fundedAccountData() },\n  // ... more accounts\n]);\n\nconst provider = new BankrunProvider(context);\nconst program = new Program<Coinflip>(IDL, provider);\n```\n\n**Devnet Integration** (real validator):\n```typescript\nconst connection = new Connection(\"https://api.devnet.solana.com\", \"confirmed\");\nconst wallet = new Wallet(keypair);\nconst provider = new AnchorProvider(connection, wallet, { commitment: \"confirmed\" });\nconst program = new Program(idl, provider);\n```\n\n**Package Scripts**:\n```json\n{\n  \"test\": \"anchor test --skip-local-validator --skip-deploy\"\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### Summary\n\nThe Solana workspace is a standard Anchor 0.32.1 setup with:\n- **2 deployed programs** (coinflip, platform) + **1 shared lib** (rng-shared)\n- **Comprehensive tests** using bankrun (no validator) with mock VRF for fast iteration\n- **Devnet integration scripts** with real Orao VRF, idempotent config initialization\n- **Feature gating** (`mock-vrf` default, `no-default-features` for devnet) to flip between test/production\n- **PDA-based accounts** with deterministic seeds for matches, configs, and player profiles\n- **IDL-driven tests** that load generated IDLs from `target/idl/` to stay in sync with program code\n\nAll keypairs are generated on-the-fly in tests; the only persistent keypairs are the program deploy keypairs in `target/deploy/`."},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: abdbec5f1280dde69 (for resuming to continue this agent's work if needed)\n<usage>total_tokens: 53997\ntool_uses: 22\nduration_ms: 63145</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"f6036e3a-bc98-4f9f-8839-caeed7dcba03","uuid":"0b284628-b83b-43ff-bec9-90e1b113f7a5","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Explore the Solana programs structure in /workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/. I need:\n\n1. The Anchor.toml configuration\n2. The test file at solana/tests/coinflip.ts (first ~100 lines to understand test setup patterns)\n3. The program IDs/keypairs used\n4. List all .so files in the target directory (if they exist)\n5. Check for any existing test scripts or bootstrap utilities in solana/\n\nProvide key file contents.","agentId":"abdbec5f1280dde69","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Now I have comprehensive information. Let me compile this into